Say '''Saint Bernard''' et kumapatya klase baley ed luyag na [[Southern Leyte]], [[Pilipinas]]. <br>  
Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 25,169 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 100.20 sq. km. Sikato et walad alenleneg  distrito. Say zip code to et 6613.
        
